en: *** Apartment - Cap Corse . Located on the 1st floor for 2 people. Kitchenette , gas stove, microwave oven , coffee maker, kettle , toaster , fridge. Private access to a terrace, equipped with a garden for lunch in the sun . Oil central heating .
it: Appartamento**** - Cap Corse. Situato al 1° piano per 2 persone. Angolo cottura, cucina a gas, forno a microonde, macchina per il caffè, bollitore, tostapane, frigorifero. Woon/eetkamer met bank en flatscreen TV. Ruime, comfortabele slaapkamer met tweepersoonsbed. Grote kledingkast. Doucheruimte.
